## Description
Looking for a simple way to manage your finances on the go? Here's your chance!
Welcome to our innovative banking mobile app - your personal financial assistant right in your pocket!
  

Why choose our app?
  

● Remote Registration: Now you can open an account from the comfort of your home by simply downloading our app and registering remotely. Afterwards, a courier will contact you and deliver the physical card.
● QR withdrawal/deposit: Easy way to make deposits and withdrawals from ATMs without a physical card via DemirBank mobile application.
● Multi-currency card: You may open a card in KGS, USD, EUR currencies allowing you to save on currency conversion, providing access to different currencies without additional fees.
● Instant payments: Using the mobile application it is possible to instantly pay for more than 300 services, including government services and fines, and make a payment when it is convenient for you in just a few clicks.
  

Download the application and enjoy new opportunities!
Demir Bank - a bank for your life!

## What’s New
Version History
21 Jul 2025
Version 5.1.48
DemirBank – your reliable financial assistant! New cool features and services are already available in the app:
  

Exclusive function for DemirBank users: automatic payment for parking at "VEFA Center" mall. Forget about looking for terminals and cash – now parking payment is available in one click!
Selecting phone numbers from your contact list is now available for all services!
The identification process has been improved.
  

Update your DemirBank app and enjoy the new features!

###  Some improvements are made, but still lots of work to do 
> Hey, I really appreciate that you joined personal and business accounts. It alone made my life much easier. But what I really want now is:
> - an ability to edit my templates
> - an ability to close my accounts
> - absence of stupid limitations. Why can’t I pay the same amount for my mobile in 24 hours? What’s the reason behind that?
> - an ability to manage my limits
> more 
Baskevich_Denis  ,  13/02/2025
###  Money transfer to other person account not working 
> Button to send money all the time is disabled, cannot press it, even all fields are correctly filled
> more 
###  Developer Response  , 
> Hello!
> Thank you for your feedback. We had some technical issues that caused this problem, but they have been quickly resolved. Currently, the system is working properly and we apologize for inconvenience.
> Demir Bank Team
> more 
akmatali  ,  14/05/2023
###  Awful design 
> I didn't like your new design. The old one was cool if compare with current. New design look old fashioned and not well done. I believe you that you can do more beautiful and comfortable then it. And some advice from me: Hear your users. I think your Bank wants to be one of the top Banks in Kyrgyzstan right? So I think one of the stepts in that way create more comfortable, stable, beautiful app then your competitors. I hope we see a new redesign soon.
> more 
###  Developer Response  , 
> Thank you for your feedback. We understand that everyone has their own preferences. We have tried to make it more user-friendly, but we will consider making changes to our design to make it more convenient.

  <p dir="ltr" data-test-bidi="">Looking for a simple way to manage your finances on the go? Here's your chance!</p>
<p dir="ltr" data-test-bidi="">Welcome to our innovative banking mobile app - your personal financial assistant right in your pocket!</p>
<br>
<p dir="ltr" data-test-bidi="">Why choose our app?</p>
<br>
<p dir="ltr" data-test-bidi="">●	Remote Registration: Now you can open an account from the comfort of your home by simply downloading our app and registering remotely. Afterwards, a courier will contact you and deliver the physical card.</p>
<p dir="ltr" data-test-bidi="">●	QR withdrawal/deposit: Easy way to make deposits and withdrawals from ATMs without a physical card via DemirBank mobile application.</p>
<p dir="ltr" data-test-bidi="">●	Multi-currency card: You may open a card in KGS, USD, EUR currencies allowing you to save on currency conversion, providing access to different currencies without additional fees.</p>
<p dir="ltr" data-test-bidi="">●	Instant payments: Using the mobile application it is possible to instantly pay for more than 300 services, including government services and fines, and make a payment when it is convenient for you in just a few clicks.</p>
<br>
<p dir="ltr" data-test-bidi="">Download the application and enjoy new opportunities!</p>
<p dir="ltr" data-test-bidi="">Demir Bank - a bank for your life!</p>
<br>
<p dir="ltr" data-test-bidi="">[:mav: 5.1.40]</p>
